# Home Lab Network Topology (Current State)

```text
INTERNET
   │
┌──────────────────────────┐
│ Xfinity Gateway / Modem  │
│ (Legacy Network Active)  │
└────────────┬─────────────┘
             │
   Ethernet Run (Upstairs → Basement)
             │
        WAN  │
┌────────────▼─────────────┐
│    OPNsense Firewall     │
│   (Qotom Mini PC)        │
│   VLAN Gateways:         │
│   99 / 60 / 30 / 20 / 40 / 50 │
│   Routing / NAT / DHCP / DNS │
└────────────┬─────────────┘
             │
        LAN / TRUNK (GE1, all VLANs tagged)
             │
┌────────────▼─────────────┐
│   Cisco SG300 L2 Switch  │
│   VLAN Distribution      │
│   (Layer 2 access only)  │
└──────┬──────┬──────┬─────┬──────┬──────┘
       │      │      │     │      │
